{
  "title": "Smnalu pnhgalan teru klegan mbasi",
  "titleCh": "部落三酸產業",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "南投縣仁愛鄉有所謂的「三酸」產業，生產在清流部落、中原部落與眉原部落。這「三酸」產業，可是很特別的產物。因此接受原民會的補助，進行專業農事教育訓練和銷售。",
      "ab": "Niqan kesun pnhgalan “Teru klegan mbasi” ka Nantoseyn Jenay Siyang, gaga alang Gluban, alang Nakahara ma alang Bgala hini. Pnhgalan “Teru klegan mbasi” nii ge, ini pntena snlmeyan ppuqun. Kiya yahun dmayo Yenminhwe pndungus tmgesa oda mhuma ma oda gnbaruy.",
